<ab facs="#facs_18_r2l20"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır vor etwıeuıl <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_18_r2l21"><expan>erb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>bottſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> von <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> bey <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>gut<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan> den </ab>
