<ab facs="#facs_18_r2l23">Die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> ob ſıch dıe ſtett <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ıht <expan>vnd<ex>er</ex>red<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
