<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde,</ex></expan> als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>gepett<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        habt, ewch <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> ze <expan>lass<ex>en,</ex></expan>
                        wie und wenn wir die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> zu
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedigst<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, des <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        künigs, dienst <expan>fertig<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>ausschik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir vor etwievil
                            <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> von <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> bey <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gut<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan>, den von Ulme, gehabt, als ir das villeiht
                        wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> mugt
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n.</expan> Die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e,</expan> ob
                        sich die stett <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> iht <expan>und
                                <ex>er</ex>red<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> eins <expan>gmeine<ex>n</ex></expan> diensts
                        aynen <expan>wurd<ex>en</ex></expan>, das <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> sie
                        uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künd<ex>en.</ex></expan> Dem
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir uns <expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        zugewartt und in dem so <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir mit
                                <expan>etlich<ex>en</ex></expan>, die die sache von des
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> diensts
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> und <add>etlicher</add>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stett frewnd
                        <expan>geworbe<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>etwas davon</add> gerett, daz wir <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> auch
                                <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> und antwurt von in
                                <expan>warte<ex>n,</ex></expan> also daz wir noch niht bedacht sein,
                        wenn wir die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ausschik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. Wer <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>, daz wir
                        hienach davon iht gewar <expan>wurd<ex>en</ex></expan>, <pb facs="#facs_19" id="9v"/>daz uns <expan>treffenl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>notdurft<ex>en</ex></expan> dewht, <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> ze
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kund<ex>en</ex></expan>, das
                            <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tun.
                        Denn wa wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
